= SDL_ReadU8 =
Use this function to read a byte from an [[SDL_RWops]].




== Syntax ==
```c++
Uint8 SDL_ReadU8(SDL_RWops* src)
```


== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''src'''
|the [[SDL_RWops]] to read from
|}


== Return Value ==
Returns the read byte on success or 0 on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.


